longBusinessSummary: Ord Mountain Resources Corp. does not have significant operations. It intends to identify and evaluate business opportunities with a view to complete a qualifying transaction. The company was formerly known as Sino Environ-Energy Tech Corp. and changed its name to Ord Mountain Resources Corp. in December 2011. Ord Mountain Resources Corp. was incorporated in 2010 and is headquartered in Port Coquitlam, Canada.
